						<summary>

						<p>The record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 881, Siddhārthi</hi> (= A.D. 959-60) and refers itself to the reign of the Noḻamba-Pallava king <hi rend="bold">Noḻambādhirāja.</hi> The <hi rend="italic">Mahājanas</hi> of a certain place (name lost) are said to have granted some land to a Vishṇu temple. The record is Damaged. </p>						

						<p>First Face.</p>						

						</summary>
